* **Applied Physics Reviews perspective** — *APR* (2025). Broad overview of ExM for biological systems. [AIP Publishing](https://pubs.aip.org/aip/apr/article/12/2/021311/3345282/Nanoscale-imaging-of-biological-systems-via)
